data.description: OWNER MOTIVATED TO SELL!!!!   Welcome to Spring Hill!      Lay your eyes on this adorable 2 bedroom, 2 bath home. This quaint home is situated on a beautiful 1/2 acre lot. Key highlights include a new roof, installed August 2021, and a 4 year old A/C unit. This home's spacious backyard is ideal for a family to enjoy. Come and watch the sunset from the lanai. NO HOA means no rules and no restrictions. Priced to sell so don’t miss out! A deal like this doesn't come around often! Home had a previous sinkhole that was professionally remediated by certified engineers over 8 years ago. Please review the attached documents.
